article_title: Obamacare's Medicaid Expansion Boosts Anthem As Individual Enrollment Slows

article_metadata.description: Anthem said its enrollment from government business, particularly from the expanded Medicaid program for poor Americans under the Affordable Care Act, fueled growth in the company’s third quarter. Anthem said its Medicaid membership was up 786,000 at the end of the third quarter to nearly 5.9 million, helping drive profits and [...]
